Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,brume0425僅分享於伊莉論壇/動畫下載區(免空)請勿任意轉載
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.68,0:00:21.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,心情不錯喔 米亞 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:23.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:25.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真會裝傻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:26.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,痛痛痛‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.24,0:00:29.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,當然會心情好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:32.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,昨天的Darling好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.82,0:00:35.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我絕不原諒傷害米亞的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:36.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這就是我的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:37.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那是我?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:42.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling遇到危機時 我會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:47.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:03.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:09.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling~ ~ ~! ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:35.53,標題,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}「哈耳庇厄和和半人馬的同居日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.15,0:02:49.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:51.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.55,0:02:53.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:56.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮是哈耳庇厄族的帕皮喲~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:59.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎 帕皮哈比帕皮?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是哈耳庇厄族的帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:05.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊‧‧‧不對 是帕比的帕皮?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:06.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕希?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怕比? 帕皮帕哈比
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:11.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮帕哈帕希
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說 妳的寄宿家庭的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,單獨行動不是被禁止的才對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以才帶你過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就因為那樣的理由把我抓過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:23.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,給我好好聽人說話!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:41.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎呀 你是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,鳥腦袋啊 ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:51.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,他們說在我記住他種族冠婚葬祭什麼的之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是不能擅自外出的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:56.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是他種族間交流法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:59.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是帕皮記不住那麼難的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:03.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以說我趁終結者不注意的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:04.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是協調員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就逃出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.54,0:04:06.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那樣不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:08.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要緊 不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.36,0:04:11.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我跑出來好多次他們都沒生氣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:15.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是‧‧‧他們說我再偷跑的話就要近親相姦什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那是什麼意思啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是遣返回國吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這不是大危機了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,危機‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.63,0:04:30.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我連一口都還沒吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,太難拿住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.31,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊啦啦 用那樣的手確實‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.31,0:04:36.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼 這個要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:38.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:44.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個 妳能自己拿著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:47.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那樣又會掉的 你幫我拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真好吃~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:57.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是 這個‧‧‧畫面簡直是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.27,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個人在做什麼呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.70,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,變態‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:02.72,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:06.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,結‧‧‧結束!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,冰淇淋就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀嗚‧‧‧黏黏糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不快點洗乾淨的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那邊有水龍頭‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳在幹什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:24.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,洗澡喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:26.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是說那個 衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:29.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你連洗澡要裸體都不知道嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,被鳥腦袋當成笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:33.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,鉤了 趕快給我出來!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:36.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:39.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在城鎮裡有洗澡的地方真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:44.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這‧‧‧這孩子 太缺乏人類社會的常識了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:48.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就算是鳥腦袋也該有個限度‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,別站著發呆  一起來玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:57.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,住手 不要把我扯進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,找到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:00.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,虧妳能找到這個地‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳這個鳥ㄚ頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:11.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不但擄走Darling 居然還做出這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,太讓人羨慕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:14.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳在說什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:18.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也想擄走Darling為愛私奔的說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳真讓人羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:22.37,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,什麼  要打架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:24.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳們兩個在幹什麼‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:26.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳這個皮包骨的鳥ㄚ頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:28.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我要把妳燉成雞湯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:31.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:33.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,白板怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳在說什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什麼說什麼 妳說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:40.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在這種地方打女子格鬥會引起圍觀的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.78,0:06:41.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀哎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,誰都沒再看‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:46.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快叫警察
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.22,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,叫消防車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:52.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,媽媽 媽媽 媽嗎‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:55.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她下不來了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這‧‧‧這有點危險吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:59.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳們兩個的裝扮才危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快把衣服穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:02.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.13,0:07:04.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒問題 交給帕皮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我去把她撞下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:06.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:17.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,翅膀吸了水 沒辦法飛起來‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要緊 這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,拉米亞族很擅長爬樹的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:34.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好 就這樣救下那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:37.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,讓Darling看看我帥氣的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:40.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說葉子好多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀哎 那女孩在哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:49.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,媽媽‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,找 ~ !到 ~ 妳 ~ 了  ! !
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:08.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,翅膀好重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是你救了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:25.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮‧‧‧做得好 了不起喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:37.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也是很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:39.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒關係 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:44.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哦啊 我聽說有小孩爬到樹上下不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:45.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好慢‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:48.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,多虧這孩子幫助 已經平安下來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的嗎 辛苦妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:56.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說回來 兩位是他種族的留學生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,寄宿家庭的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:00.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我身邊有Darling在‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:03.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊 我要被近親相姦了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,都說了是遣返回國!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:07.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就是說妳要被趕出這個國家了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦~~!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,難不成‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:16.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:18.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我就是她寄宿家庭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:21.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她們兩個都寄宿在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:23.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:26.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼請你出示證明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,完蛋了 !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:43.88,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,難道說說你沒有證明‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:45.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,證明在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:50.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀! 真是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:54.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳是如何在那麼短的時間準備好證明的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,證明書原本就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.67,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦 為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:04.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為這個逃跑慣犯找不到寄宿家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:07.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以正打算把她推給Darling君‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:12.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,拜託給你照顧結果中途被她跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:15.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,讓帕皮跑掉的協調員是墨須小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:16.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:22.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就是這樣帕皮 這裡就是妳的新家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:23.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:28.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,他至少也是這家的主人 妳要好好聽他的話喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:32.23,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,好‧‧‧好‧‧‧好‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:32.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可以兩個人同時寄宿在一個家庭裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:36.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐真的有夠隨意的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:40.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼帕皮妳可不能再逃跑了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:41.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮雖然不懂太複雜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過有一件事記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:51.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,從今後只要一直跟主人再一起就行了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請多關照 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.41,0:10:55.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主人 我們去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:56.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,繼續剛才的洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:11:00.39,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,繼續‧‧‧繼續‧‧‧繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:10:59.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,別拉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:03.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:07.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼Darling就麻煩你給帕皮洗澡囉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.37,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,喔 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:09.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:10.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,小心別感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.04,0:11:14.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞 意外的冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:15.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我還以為妳會反對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.72,0:11:19.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,又‧‧‧又不是什麼大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:22.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,跟Darling住在同一個屋簷下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:25.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,突然有人礙事稍微有點不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:28.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但帕皮只不過是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且就是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再怎麼說也還是個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:33.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以我要表現出大人的從容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:36.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎啦 帕皮和米亞同年齡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:42.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哈耳庇厄族是為了在天空飛翔才進化成幼小體型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:44.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,其實外表和年齡的差別是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:50.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 還是我來幫她洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:56.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,聽好了 Darling可是我的Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,對她出手的話我可不會饒妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:01.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮 又沒有手哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:03.32,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:06.26,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,我的Darling要是有個萬一我可不饒妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:07.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我的身體還承受的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:11.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}魔物娘!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:17.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}魔物娘!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:42.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒想到一大早就要去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:46.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不光是米亞 帕皮也很會吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我家的家計真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:04.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒想到真的遇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,簡直就是命運!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.24,0:13:09.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,吾乃珊卓雷雅‧夏努斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:11.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是高貴的半人馬族
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:14.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你就是命運中會成為吾主公的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.37,0:13:20.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓雷雅?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:24.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,組織特別允許她單獨行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.43,0:13:31.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為半人馬族似乎有自己尋找主公的傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:32.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主公?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:35.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大概就是寄宿家庭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.75,0:13:40.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,畢竟 留學中‧‧‧要寄宿家庭‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:47.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不好意思了 我今天休假‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:50.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她的事就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:53.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧墨須小‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:58.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的 真隨意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:01.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,說起來日本的魔咒不可小覷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,魔咒?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:04.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,全力跑向十字路口
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:07.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,遇到相撞就能與命運之人結合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:09.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這是日本自古以來的魔咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:12.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳這樣做只是單純的交通事故而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我差點就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是‧‧‧是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:18.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再說 我也不是妳命運中的那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:22.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且那不是魔咒而是漫畫的橋段 已過時了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什‧‧‧什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我果然應該咬著一片土司的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:28.55,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,遲到了 要遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:30.72,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳這些知識是從哪裡學來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:34.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再說 妳為什麼要在一大早找命運之人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且還用這種粗暴的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯~這是因為‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,閃開 閃開 閃開!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.72,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:48.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可惡 還想要加深罪孽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呼吸要‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:15:00.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那傢伙就是最近擾亂這一帶的飛車搶匪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:05.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,作為尊貴的半人馬 我不能袖手旁觀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:09.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,以吾之劍起誓 非要抓住那飛車搶匪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:15.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是根據他種族間交流法 我不能對那傢伙出手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:19.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以在尋找能與我並肩作戰的命運中的主公
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:22.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在此之前妳已經違反槍刀管制法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:24.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是也沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:26.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你不是我主公也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:28.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,跟我一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我知道啦 知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:33.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那我就坐上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:36.66,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:39.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你做什麼 我可不是馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然你不是我的主公 就請不要做無禮的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:47.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的 日本的魔咒果然不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:49.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那要怎樣跟妳一起去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.14,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,這次收穫不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,到此為止了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:03.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大膽小賊 快點束手就擒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:08.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不然就休怪吾手上利劍不留情面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,聽好了! 要是敢摸奇怪的地方我就把你打下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:14.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那就放慢點速度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,剛才的馬女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,三十六計走為上策
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:20.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:23.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,安全駕駛啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,摔下去 要摔下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,別亂動 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:47.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,雕蟲小技 就這點本事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:00.33,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,BYE BYE喲 馬女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,傲慢的傢伙 就這點程度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.21,0:17:05.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,休想逃跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:25.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂 你這傢伙快替我把他‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還以為要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:33.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你再摸哪裡啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:34.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳不要亂動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 是故意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.81,0:17:42.58,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,要摔下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:43.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:47.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不僅騎在我身上還讓我受此羞辱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,待會你會怎樣‧‧‧給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:06.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂 石化了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:16.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可惡 居然敢任意妄為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:19.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,將我的胸‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:26.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.31,0:18:30.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 我要用你的血祭劍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:40.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳‧‧‧妳這個馬女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:42.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,變成生馬片吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:51.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:59.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我以為是這樣 結果沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:02.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,原來是仿造刀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:05.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼可能讓她帶著真劍到處逛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:08.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,去逮捕飛車搶匪 真是太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:11.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不  並不是喜歡才去做的‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:14.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是珊卓雷雅說要追摩托車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.12,0:19:15.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,摩托車?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:18.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你該不會坐到她身上了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:22.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,決定追隨一生的主公才能騎在自己身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這可是半人馬一族的鐵則
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:30.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘛 對於她來說 大概就類似結婚吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:33.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果你強行乘坐上去的話 那相當於‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.09,0:19:35.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,相‧‧‧相當於?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:37.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就相當於是強暴一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:40.19,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊 我的炒麵!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.91,0:19:50.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉 珊卓雷雅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:53.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我對如此重大的事情我並不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:55.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我絕對沒有任何惡意的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:19:58.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓雷雅?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.58,0:20:06.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不是珊卓雷雅 希望你能叫我賽蕾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:09.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,親近的人都這樣叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:10.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,其實應該受到責備的人是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:16.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我把你也捲入了自己的正義感之中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:19.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且 還讓你受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:22.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不 再說我也有沒拒絕妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:25.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳不用這麼責備自己‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,並沒有那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:29.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你也能感受到我劇烈的心跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:32.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我現在正感受到命運!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:38.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒錯!就像是希臘神話中的英雄海格拉斯和賢者凱隆相遇一般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:42.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,日本的魔咒真是厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:46.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的能和命運中的主公相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:49.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,自從來到這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:52.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不 是自我出生以來第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:56.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,像這樣‧‧‧被人挺身來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:21:01.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以 吾 珊卓雷雅 ‧ 夏努斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:06.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,承認汝為吾主 在此發誓向汝終生忠誠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:12.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主公 你願意接受我的這份忠誠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,賽‧‧‧賽蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:19.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling你又在外面帶女人回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.57,0:21:21.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,主人 我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.89,0:21:24.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling!? 這些女人是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:26.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,太不檢點了 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:29.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 那傷是怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:30.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,飯還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:37.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然我來了就不能像以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:40.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,凡事都要將主人放在第一位來考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:42.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我一直都把Darling放在第一位來考慮的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:45.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮也有考慮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:49.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼誰來幫我做一下家事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.38,0:23:24.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\c&HA0CCF9&}抓住你了 這次不會讓你跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:24.94,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,主人 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:27.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\c&HA0CCF9&}Darling可是命中注定要跟我結婚的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:29.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\c&HA0CCF9&}主人是要跟帕皮結婚的
