Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.27,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,Monster Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:19.92,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,MonMonMonMon Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:23.44,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,Monster Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.45,0:01:29.26,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,MonMonMonMon Monster’S life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.56,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其一、不要在意他人的目光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.56,0:01:41.12,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,要大膽的、以及慎重的選擇目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:43.66,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其二、日常問候要適度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:47.14,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,當做好心理準備的話、就上陣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:50.90,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其三、發現機會就要迅速瞄準
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.99,0:01:52.53,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,開火開火開火開火!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.54,0:01:55.02,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,其四、不需要去顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.90,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,最後確實給目標的心致命一擊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:02.61,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,只要有愛的話、就算只有一分也足夠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:08.83,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,比那個更重要的是、遵循慾望的指引、
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:11.84,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,衝吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:14.45,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘿! 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:17.26,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為有你在所以才會是最強的是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:19.89,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果能一直在一起那就是最棒的不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:22.42,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,無論前方會遇到什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:25.22,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,只要和你就 All OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.23,0:02:27.79,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,如今以無庸置疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:30.53,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,這肯定就是宇宙第一的愛對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:34.91,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,等不及你的答案、我已經
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:39.78,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,最高速墬入愛河!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:39.78,OP-TN,brume0425,0,0,0,,
